European Team Championship (2019), Batumi GEO, rd 9, Nov-02
Queen's Gambit Declined: Austrian Defense (D06)

1. d4 d5 2. c4 c5 3. cd5 Qd5 4. Nf3 cd4 5. Nc3 Qa5 6. Nd4 Nf6 7. Bd2 e5 8. Ndb5 Bb4 9. a3 Bc3 10. Nd6 Ke7 11. Bc3 Qd5 12. Bb4 Nc6 13. Nc8 Ke6 14. g3 Qh1 15. Qd6 Kf5 16. Qd3 e4 17. Nd6 Kg6 18. Follow games live here https://chess24.com/en/watch/live-tournaments/fide-world-fischer-random-chess-championship-2019

The 22nd European Team Championship is a 9-round Swiss tournament taking place from 24 October to 2 November 2019 in Batumi, Georgia.

Players receive 90 minutes for 40 moves, followed by 30 minutes to the end of the game, plus a 30-second increment starting from move one. Official website: euro2019.ge
